Review: The husband is my favorite character in the movie by far. He captures something so essentially human, the strength of the narrative that we form about the self and the ones closest to us, or even a sense of meaning in our own narrative, that I feel is rarely stated in such an explicit way. Great and heartwarming! And lovely!
